== 辛丑の月 ==
In a Western calendar year whose last digit is either 1 or 6 (corresponding to the Heavenly Stems {{ill|Xin|ja|辛}} and {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)}}), the month of December becomes the Yin Metal Ox month. (Note that here “month” may refer either to the month of the old calendar or to a seasonal month defined from {{ill|Xiaohan|ja|小寒}} until the day before {{ill|Lichun|ja|立春}}.)

