=== 出来事 ===
* In {{ill|Guangxu|ja|光緒|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 27th Year and {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 34th Year (1901 AD) – The {{ill|Beijing Protocol|ja|辛丑和約|lt=Beijing Protocol|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, concerning the Boxer Rebellion (excluding Russia) among a coalition of 11 countries (including Austria, Britain, and France) and the Qing Empire, was signed.
== 辛丑の月 ==
In a Western calendar year whose last digit is either 1 or 6 (corresponding to the Heavenly Stems {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}), the month of December becomes the Yin Metal Ox month. (Note that here “month” may refer either to the month of the old calendar or to a seasonal month defined from {{ill|Xiaohan|ja|小寒|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Lichun|ja|立春|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.)

== 辛丑の日 ==
=== 選日 ===
The Yin Metal Ox day is the 9th day of {{ill|Tian Yi Tian Shang|ja|天一天上|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
