== 辛丑の月 ==
In a Western calendar year whose last digit is either 1 or 6 (corresponding to the Heavenly Stems {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=}} and {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=}}), the month of December becomes the Yin Metal Ox month. (Note that here “month” may refer either to the month of the old calendar or to a seasonal month defined from {{ill|Xiaohan|ja|小寒|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xiaohan|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Lichun|ja|立春|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lichun|qq=}}.)

