=== Events === * In {{ill|Guangxu|ja|光緒|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Guangxu|qq=}} 27th Year and [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 34th Year (1901 AD) – The {{ill|Beijing Protocol|ja|辛丑和約|lt=Beijing Protocol|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Beijing Protocol|qq=}}, concerning the Boxer Rebellion (excluding Russia) among a coalition of 11 countries (including Austria, Britain, and France) and the Qing Empire, was signed. == Months == In a Western calendar year whose last digit is either 1 or 6 (corresponding to the Heavenly Stems {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|lt=Kanoto (辛)|2=ja|3=辛|4=zh|5=辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=}} and {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|lt=Hinoe (丙)|2=ja|3=丙|4=zh|5=丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=}}), the month of December becomes the Yin Metal Ox month. (Note that here “month” may refer either to the month of the old calendar or to a seasonal month defined from [[:en:Xiaohan|Xiaohan]] until the day before [[:en:Lichun|Risshun]].)
== Days == === 選日 === The Yin Metal Ox day is the 9th day of {{ill|Tian Yi Tian Shang|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tian Yi Tian Shang|qq=}}. == See Also == * {{prefix|qq=}} * {{intitle|qq=}}
