{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Metal Ox|kanji=辛丑|romaji=kanoto ushi|onyomi=shinchū|p=xīnchǒu|w=hsin-ch'ou|mi=ɕin⁵³ ʈʂʰoʊ̯|y=san1 chau2|j=san1 chau2|ci=sɐn tsʰɐu̯|mc=sin tʂʰjuw|oc-bs=sin ʈʂʰuʔ|qq=}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}} '''Yin Metal Ox''' (辛丑) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|Sexagenary cycle|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.
It is the 38th combination in the Sexagenary cycle, preceded by {{ill|Gengzi|ja|1=Yang Metal Rat|2=ja|庚子|1=Yang Metal Rat|lt=Gengzi|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gengzi|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Renyin|ja|1=Yang Water Tiger|2=ja|壬寅|lt=Renyin|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Renyin|qq=}}. In the {{ill|Yin-Yang Five Elements philosophy|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang Five Elements philosophy|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the Heavenly Stem {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|lt=Kanoto (辛)|2=ja|3=辛|4=zh|5=辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=}} represents yin metal and the Earthly Branch {{ill|Chou|ja|丑|1=Ox (Zodiac)|lt=Ox (丑)|2=ja|3=丑|1=Ox (zodiac)|lt=Ox (丑)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chou|13=User:Immanuelle/Ox (zodiac)|qq=}} represents yin earth; according to the theory of mutual generation (土生金) in the Five Elements philosophy, earth generates metal.
==Pronunciation== ==Years of Yin Metal Ox== A year is designated as a Yin Metal Ox year when the Western calendar year divided by 60 leaves a remainder of 41. {| class="wikitable" |+ '''Years of Yin Metal Ox''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 41|41 AD]] * [[:en:AD 101|101 AD]] * [[:en:161|161 AD]] * [[:en:221|221 AD]] * [[:en:281|281 AD]] * [[:en:341|341 AD]] * [[:en:401|401 AD]] * [[:en:461|461 AD]] * [[:en:521|521 AD]] * [[:en:581|581 AD]] * [[:en:641|641 AD]] * [[:en:701|701 AD]] * [[:en:761|761 AD]] * [[:en:821|821 AD]] * [[:en:881|881 AD]] * [[:en:941|941 AD]] | * [[:en:1001|1001 AD]] * [[:en:1061|1061 AD]] * [[:en:1121|1121 AD]] * [[:en:1181|1181 AD]] * [[:en:1241|1241 AD]] * [[:en:1301|1301 AD]] * [[:en:1361|1361 AD]] * [[:en:1421|1421 AD]] * [[:en:1481|1481 AD]] * [[:en:1541|1541 AD]] * [[:en:1601|1601 AD]] * [[:en:1661|1661 AD]] * [[:en:1721|1721 AD]] * [[:en:1781|1781 AD]] * [[:en:1841|1841 AD]] * [[:en:1901|1901 AD]] * [[:en:1961|1961 AD]] | * [[:en:2021|2021 AD]] * {{ill|2081 AD|ja|2081年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2081 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2141 AD|ja|2141年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2141 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2201 AD|ja|2201年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2201 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2261 AD|ja|2261年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2261 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2321 AD|ja|2321年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2321 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2381 AD|ja|2381年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2381 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2441 AD|ja|2441年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2441 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2501 AD|ja|2501年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2501 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2561 AD|ja|2561年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2561 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2621 AD|ja|2621年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2621 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2681 AD|ja|2681年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2681 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2741 AD|ja|2741年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2741 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2801 AD|ja|2801年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2801 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2861 AD|ja|2861年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2861 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2921 AD|ja|2921年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2921 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2981 AD|ja|2981年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2981 AD|qq=}} |}
=== Events === * In {{ill|Guangxu|ja|光緒|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Guangxu|qq=}} 27th Year and [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 34th Year (1901 AD) – The {{ill|Beijing Protocol|ja|辛丑和約|lt=Beijing Protocol|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Beijing Protocol|qq=}}, concerning the Boxer Rebellion (excluding Russia) among a coalition of 11 countries (including Austria, Britain, and France) and the Qing Empire, was signed. ==Months of Yin Metal Ox== In a Western calendar year whose last digit is either 1 or 6 (corresponding to the Heavenly Stems {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|lt=Kanoto (辛)|2=ja|3=辛|4=zh|5=辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=}} and {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|lt=Hinoe (丙)|2=ja|3=丙|4=zh|5=丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=}}), the month of December becomes the Yin Metal Ox month. (Note that here “month” may refer either to the month of the old calendar or to a seasonal month defined from [[:en:Xiaohan|Xiaohan]] until the day before [[:en:Lichun|Risshun]].)
==Days of Yin Metal Ox== === 選日 === The Yin Metal Ox day is the 9th day of {{ill|Tian Yi Tian Shang|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tian Yi Tian Shang|qq=}}. == See Also == * {{prefix|qq=}} * {{intitle|qq=}}
